<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Terms and Conditions - Driver App</title>

  <style>
   /* =========================================
   ASIAA TRAVEL - BRIGHT YELLOW THEME
========================================= */

@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap');

*{
  margin:0;
  padding:0;
  box-sizing:border-box;
}

body{
  font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at top left,#fff3c4,transparent 35%),
    radial-gradient(circle at bottom right,#ffe082,transparent 35%),
    linear-gradient(135deg,#fffdf5,#fff8e1,#fffde7);
  min-height:100vh;
  padding:40px 20px;
  color:#2b2b2b;
}

/* =========================================
   MAIN CONTAINER
========================================= */

.policy-container{
  max-width:1100px;
  margin:auto;
  border-radius:30px;
  overflow:hidden;
  border:1px solid #ffe082;
  backdrop-filter:blur(12px);
  box-shadow:
    0 12px 35px rgba(255,193,7,0.18),
    0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
}

/* =========================================
   HEADER
========================================= */

.policy-header{
  position:relative;
  padding:90px 50px;
  text-align:center;
  overflow:hidden;
  background:
    linear-gradient(135deg,#ffd54f,#ffc107,#ffca28);
}

.policy-header::before{
  content:"";
  position:absolute;
  width:420px;
  height:420px;
  border-radius:50%;
  background:#ffffff30;
  top:-220px;
  right:-120px;
}

.policy-header::after{
  content:"";
  position:absolute;
  width:280px;
  height:280px;
  border-radius:50%;
  background:#fff9c433;
  bottom:-150px;
  left:-80px;
}

.policy-header h1{
  position:relative;
  z-index:2;
  font-size:60px;
  font-weight:700;
  color:#4e342e;
  margin-bottom:12px;
  letter-spacing:1px;
}

.policy-header p{
  position:relative;
  z-index:2;
  color:#5d4037;
  font-size:17px;
  font-weight:500;
}

/* =========================================
   CONTENT AREA
========================================= */

.policy-content{
  padding:50px;
}

/* =========================================
   POLICY SECTIONS
========================================= */

.policy-section{
  margin-bottom:30px;
  padding:30px;
  border-radius:24px;
  background:#fffdf7;
  border:1px solid #ffe082;
  transition:0.35s ease;
}

.policy-section:hover{
  transform:translateY(-5px);
  box-shadow:0 12px 28px rgba(255,193,7,0.15);
  border-color:#ffc107;
}

.policy-section h2{
  font-size:25px;
  margin-bottom:18px;
  font-weight:700;
  color:#ff9800;
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  gap:12px;
}

.policy-section h2::before{
  content:"";
  width:12px;
  height:12px;
  border-radius:50%;
  background:#ffc107;
  box-shadow:0 0 14px #ffc107;
}

.policy-section p{
  color:#555;
  font-size:15.5px;
  line-height:1.9;
}

.policy-section ul{
  margin-top:16px;
  padding-left:18px;
}

.policy-section ul li{
  margin-bottom:14px;
  color:#444;
}

/* =========================================
   HIGHLIGHT BOX
========================================= */

.highlight-box{
  margin-top:18px;
  padding:22px;
  border-radius:18px;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,#fff9c4,#fff3b0);
  border:1px solid #ffd54f;
  color:#5d4037;
  font-weight:500;
}

/* =========================================
   CONTACT BOX
========================================= */

.contact-box{
  margin-top:22px;
  padding:24px;
  border-radius:20px;
  border:1px solid #ffe082;
}

.contact-box strong{
  color:#ff9800;
}

/* =========================================
   FOOTER
========================================= */

.footer-note{
  text-align:center;
  padding:28px;
  border-top:1px solid #ffe082;
  color:#666;
  font-size:14px;
  background:#fff8e1;
}

/* =========================================
   SCROLLBAR
========================================= */

::-webkit-scrollbar{
  width:8px;
}

::-webkit-scrollbar-track{
  background:#fff8e1;
}

::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{
  background:#ffc107;
  border-radius:30px;
}

/* =========================================
   RESPONSIVE
========================================= */

@media(max-width:768px){

  body{
    padding:20px 12px;
  }

  .policy-header{
    padding:70px 25px;
  }

  .policy-header h1{
    font-size:40px;
  }

  .policy-content{
    padding:24px;
  }

  .policy-section{
    padding:22px;
  }

  .policy-section h2{
    font-size:21px;
  }

  .policy-section p,
  .policy-section li{
    font-size:14px;
  }
}
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="policy-container">

    <div class="policy-header">
      <h1>Terms and Conditions</h1>
      <p>Last Updated: May 2026</p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section">
      <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
      <p>
        This terms and conditions explains how we collect, use, store, and protect
        the personal information of drivers using our Driver Application.
        By using the App, you agree to the collection and use of information
        in accordance with this policy.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section">
      <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>

      <ul>
        <li>Full name, phone number, email address</li>
        <li>Driver’s license details</li>
        <li>Vehicle registration and insurance documents</li>
        <li>Government-issued identity proof</li>
        <li>Trip and location data</li>
        <li>Payment and transaction details</li>
        <li>Device and app usage information</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section">
      <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>

      <ul>
        <li>To create and manage driver accounts</li>
        <li>To verify identity and documents</li>
        <li>To provide transportation services</li>
        <li>To process payments and commissions</li>
        <li>To improve app performance and safety</li>
        <li>To communicate updates and notifications</li>
        <li>To prevent fraud and illegal activities</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section">
      <h2>5. Sharing of Information</h2>

      <p>
        We do not sell personal information. However, we may share information:
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>With customers during ride services</li>
        <li>With payment service providers</li>
        <li>With government authorities when legally required</li>
        <li>With third-party verification or security partners</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section">
      <h2>6. Data Security</h2>

      <p>
        We implement reasonable security measures to protect your data from
        unauthorized access, misuse, disclosure, or alteration.
        However, no online system is completely secure.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section">
      <h2>7. Data Retention</h2>

      <p>
        We retain personal and trip information for as long as necessary
        to provide services, comply with legal obligations,
        resolve disputes, and enforce agreements.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section">
      <h2>8. Driver Rights</h2>

      <ul>
        <li>Access your personal data</li>
        <li>Request correction of inaccurate information</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your account</li>
        <li>Withdraw consent where applicable</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section">
      <h2>9. Third-Party Services</h2>

      <p>
        The App may contain integrations with third-party services such as
        payment gateways, maps, analytics, or communication tools.
        We are not responsible for their independent privacy practices.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section">
      <h2>10. Children’s Privacy</h2>

      <p>
        The App is not intended for individuals under the age of 18.
        We do not knowingly collect personal information from minors.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section">
      <h2>11. Policy Updates</h2>

      <p>
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time.
        Continued use of the App after changes means you accept the updated policy.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section">
      <h2>12. Contact Us</h2>

      <p>
        If you have any questions regarding this Privacy Policy,
        you may contact us at:
      </p>

      <div class="highlight-box">
        <strong>Email:</strong> support@asiaa-travel.com <br>
        <strong>Phone:</strong> +91 9514228005 <br>
        <strong>Company:</strong> Asiaa Travel
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-note">
      © 2026 Asiaa Travel. All Rights Reserved.
    </div>

  </div>

</body>
</html>